title: Alaska The Last Frontier Season 1 and 2 Complete
description:
This is the complete Season 1 and 2 (all episodes as of June 2013) of Alaska The Last Frontier. The last 5 episodes have been sometimes mistakenly uploaded as Season 3, but there was just a hiatus in Season 2.

Season 1 - 3 episodes
Season 2 - 15 episodes

These are of varying resolutions, but all very watchable. I think they're pretty much all 480p or thereabouts. But I watch them on my 55" 1080p LED with no issues at all.

Enjoy!
